{"ID":270227, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"227\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs226.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs228.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 227<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">being your associates. Females, if they are pure<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> and innocent, can come in the presence of God;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span>\n  for what is more pleasing to God<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> than innocence; you must be innocent,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> or you cannot come up\n  before God; if we would come before God, we must keep ourselves pure, as He is pure.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Devil&rsquo;s Power to Deceive<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The devil has great power to deceive;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> he will so transform things as to make one gape at those\n  who are doing the will of God.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> You need not be teasing your husbands because of their deeds, but\n  let the weight of your innocence, kindness and affection be felt, which is more mighty than a\n  millstone hung about the neck;<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> not war, not jangle, not contradiction, or dispute, but meekness,\n  love, purity&mdash;these are the things that should magnify you in the eyes of all good men. Achan [see\n  Joshua 7]<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> must be brought to light, iniquity must be purged<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> out from the midst of the Saints; then\n  the veil will be rent,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> and the blessings of heaven<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> will flow down&mdash;they will roll down like the\n  Mississippi river.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If this Society listen to the counsel<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> of the Almighty, through the heads of the Church,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> they\n  shall have power to command queens in their midst.<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I now deliver it as a prophecy, if the inhabitants of this state, with the people of the surrounding\n  country, will turn unto the Lord with all their hearts,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> ten years will not roll around before the kings\n  and queens of the earth will come unto Zion,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and pay their respects to the leaders of this people;\n  they shall come with their millions, and shall contribute of their abundance for the relief of the poor,\n  and the building up and beautifying of Zion.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">After this instruction, you will be responsible for your own sins;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> it is a desirable honor that\n  you should so walk before our heavenly Father<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> as to save yourselves;<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> we are all responsible to\n  God for the manner we improve the light<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> and wisdom given by our Lord to enable us to save\n  ourselves.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Beware of Self-Righteousness<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">President Smith continued reading from the above-mentioned chapter,<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> and to give instructions\n  respecting the order of God,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> as established in the Church, saying everyone should aspire only to\n  magnify his own office and calling.<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110020\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110020)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110020)\">1 Tim. 5:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107819\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107819)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107819)\">Matt. 5:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115104\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115104)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115104)\">D&amp;C 97:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110939\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110939)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110939)\">1 Ne. 6:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111367\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111367)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111367)\">Jacob 2:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106672\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106672)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106672)\">Ps. 26:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115046\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115046)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115046)\">D&amp;C 93:38<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115307\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115307)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115307)\">D&amp;C 104:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106667\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106667)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106667)\">Ps. 24:3-4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110595\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110595)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110595)\">1 Jn. 3:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113649\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113649)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113649)\">D&amp;C 38:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112976\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=